summary: This is a business records affidavit from a TD Bank, N.A. custodian of records, sworn on August 27, 2019, certifying the authenticity of attached bank records related to case 2019R01059. It establishes the foundation for admitting financial records as evidence.

events.title: Affidavit Execution
events.description: A custodian of records for TD Bank, N.A. swears to and subscribes an affidavit before a notary public, certifying the authenticity of attached bank records.

keyFacts: The document is a business records affidavit from TD Bank, N.A., related to case 2019R01059.
The affidavit was sworn and subscribed on August 27, 2019, by a custodian of records for the bank.
The affiant certifies that attached bank records are true and accurate copies kept in the regular course of business.
The affidavit serves as a foundational document to admit financial records as evidence in a legal proceeding.
